              left = this.visit(node.children[0], value);
              right = this.visit(node.children[1], left);
              return right;
            case "Index":
              if (!isArray(value)) {
                return null;
              }

              if (index < 0) {

              var computed = this.computeSliceParams(value.length, sliceParams);
              var start = computed[0];
              var stop = computed[1];
              var step = computed[2];

                  for (i = start; i < stop; i += step) {
                      result.push(value[i]);
                  }
              } else {
